Firmware for rpiaddon device

The rpiaddon is a Raspberry Pi Add On board by Damian Melson.
See
https://forum.fhem.de/index.php/topic,14156.html
for details.

FLASHING FIRMWARE

To update firmware with a-culfw execute:

	make clean
	make program

on the raspberry pi. This will require some tools installed upfront. 
Use:

	apt-get install make avrdude

to flash the recompiled rpiaddon.hex file.

USING

The a-culfw stack is available on: /dev/ttyAMA0@38400